[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Are there good examples from other 
[normal]countries that could be applied in the UK?
[normal]              
[normal]              
[normal]              
[normal]Yes, but not always of the sort that back up the government's assumption of the need for miles of
[normal]              
[normal]              
[normal]              
[normal]new
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]roads in a country that "Action for
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Roads" freely admits to be compact by comparison with much
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]              
[normal]              
[normal]              
[normal]of
[normal] el
[normal]sewhere
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]in Europe. To take just two examples:
[normal]&#xa0;
