[normal]              
[normal]NECTAR is an open, voluntary, umbrella body, established to provide a forum in which the many organisations with a
[normal]n
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]              
[normal]interest
[normal] in
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]sustainable
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]transport in all its forms can develop a co-ordinated view on contemporary transport issues.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]              
[normal]NECTAR provides
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]opportunity
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]for the exchange of news, studies and information.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]              
[normal]The NECTAR area of interest covers the North-East 
[normal]of England from the North Sea coast to the Pennines, and stretches
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]              
[normal]from
[normal]&#xa0;
